FINANCIAL BRIEF: For the fiscal year ended 31 December 2016, Be Think Solve Execute SpA revenues increased 19% to EUR135.6M. Net income increased 23% to EUR4.2M. Revenues reflect Consulting segment increase of 28% to EUR102.2M, Corporate segment increase of 11% to EUR4.3M. Net income benefited from IT Services segment income increase from EUR80K to EUR1.8M, Consulting segment income increase of 15% to EUR12.1M.  more » 










  
